    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Oh, maybe we're trying to read the settings from the URL but failing in Safari, resulting in empty an empty index in the next query.\n\nNot using the hash notation means that we cannot share URI between old and modern browsers. I think we should at least be able to read the URI parameters in Safari, even if we do not use the History API to write them back.\n",
