    "body": "To complement the issue, here are the step to reproduce : \n- open https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/examples/media/\n- url is updated with infos from the search state (query parameters)\n- in Safari the idx url parameter contains nothing, in the other browsers it contains the name of the currently used index (and this is the expected behavior)\n",
